import { Nav, Container, Image, Row, Col, Form, NavDropdown, Navbar, Button, NavLink } from "react-bootstrap";
import logo from './img/magazine.svg';

const HeaderApp = () => {
    return (


        <Container fluid>
            <Row>
                <Col xs={2} md={2} lg={2}>
                </Col>
                <Col  xs={1} md={1} lg={1}>
                    <Nav.Link>
                        Home
                    </Nav.Link>
                </Col>
                <Col  xs={1} md={1} lg={1}>
                    <Nav.Link>
                        Post
                    </Nav.Link>
                </Col>
                <Col  xs={2} md={2} lg={2}>
                    <NavDropdown title='Category'>
                        <NavDropdown.Item>PC</NavDropdown.Item>
                        <NavDropdown.Item>Mobile</NavDropdown.Item>
                        <NavDropdown.Item>Console</NavDropdown.Item>
                    </NavDropdown>
                </Col>
                <input placeholder="Search"></input>
                <button>Search</button>
                <Col>
                    <Nav.Link>
                        Login
                    </Nav.Link>
                </Col>
                <Col>
                    <Nav.Link>
                        Sign-up
                    </Nav.Link>
                </Col>

            </Row>
        </Container>

    );
}

export default HeaderApp;
